description: TJ Young has martial arts experience and a polite demeanor. Too bad he's matched up with brute brawler Dak Ramsey! TJ is looking forward to a good match and is used to the controlled sparring ring of a martial arts studio. Dak is used to bar fights where it's all about doing whatever it takes before getting caught. But what will happen when both fighters' believe their strengths to be on the ground? The prevalence of slams, holds, chokes, submissions, and hard cocks in this fight make it one to definitely not miss.
title: TJ Young vs Dak Ramsey
